"{\"uid\": \"thehindu.com-news-international-south-korea-deploys-sniffer-dog-to-screen-for-bedbugs-off-those-returning-after-paris-olympics-article68515768.ece\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"October 20, 2025e-Paper  The View From IndiaLooking at World Affairs from the Indian perspective.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 97, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 84, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9027287950982633, \"rank\": 0.10371599502371372, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First Day First ShowNews and reviews from the world of cinema and streaming.\", \"from\": 99, \"to\": 175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today's CacheYour download of the top 5 technology stories of the day.\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Science For AllThe weekly newsletter from science writers takes the jargon out of science and puts the fun in!\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jargon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"jargon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jargon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jargon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Data PointDecoding the headlines with facts, figures, and numbers  Health MattersRamya Kannan writes to you on getting to good health, and staying there  The Hindu On BooksBooks of the week, reviews, excerpts, new titles and features.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"October 20, 2025e-Paper  Published- August 12, 2024 03:23 pm IST - INCHEON, South Korea  Ceco, South Korea's first bedbug sniffing dog, demonstrates bed bug detection on luggage at Incheon International Airport in Incheon, South Korea                                           | Photo Credit: via Reuters  South Korea has deployed a bedbug sniffer dog at its main Incheon international airport in a bid to reduce the risk of the tiny insects entering the country when athletes, officials and fans return fromthe Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996282934778228, \"rank\": 0.00037184473810772, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996282934778228, \"rank\": 0.00037184473810772, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\", \"score\": 0.5697108536808656, \"rank\": 0.7552730057988797, \"text\": \"Incheon\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\"}, {\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996282934778228, \"rank\": 0.00037184473810772, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999970864337, \"rank\": 2.9134963303713382e-09, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996282934778228, \"rank\": 0.00037184473810772, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Incheon international airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\"}, {\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leading the campaign is a two-year-old beagle named Ceco, who pest control company Cesco said is the first and so far only canine trained in the country to detect the odour of pheromones, the chemicals released by bedbugs.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ceco is capable of sweeping a standard hotel room in under two minutes, company official Kim Min-su said.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pest control company has teamed up with South Korea's ministries of security and transportation, as well as the Disease Control and Prevention Agency, and is working with airlines and Incheon airport to screen travellers on arrival.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1501, \"end\": 1512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996282934778228, \"rank\": 0.00037184473810772, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\", \"score\": 0.5697108536808656, \"rank\": 0.7552730057988797, \"text\": \"Incheon\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, authorities in Paris raced to contain a nationwide panic over bedbugs as the city geared up for the Olympics, worried that the tiny wingless critters might ruin the event and conducted a campaign to root out any infestation.\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987330739, \"rank\": 1.2668117158679234e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As the global community is gathering in Paris, France, on the occasion of the 2024 Summer Olympic Games, there is a chance bedbugs will enter the country following the event,\\\" a government press release said.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987330739, \"rank\": 1.2668117158679234e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1980, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9965782630497175, \"rank\": 0.0029448118160307806, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Therefore, we are taking a preemptive response to intercept the entry through the Incheon international airport, which is the main gateway to the country.\\\"\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2226, \"end\": 2255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Incheon international airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incheon_International_Airport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ceco and his team were deployed on Friday as more athletes and officials started arriving from Paris and will continue to work through to Sept. 8, the government said.\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2396, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987330739, \"rank\": 1.2668117158679234e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Korea sent 144 athletes competing to the Olympics in Paris, which ended on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2470, \"end\": 2481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996282934778228, \"rank\": 0.00037184473810772, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987330739, \"rank\": 1.2668117158679234e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flights arriving directly from Paris are being disinfected once a week compared to a rate of once a month normally, and the airport quarantine service is being prepared to swing into action if an outbreak is detected in an aircraft or the airport.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987330739, \"rank\": 1.2668117158679234e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Korea also went through a period of national hysteria in 2023 after reports of suspected infestations at micro-apartments, motel rooms and a traditional spa called a \\\"jjimjilbang\\\" and conducted a widespread disinfection campaign.d)  Published- August 12, 2024 03:23 pm IST  Paris Olympics 2024/South Korea/Olympics/Offbeat  Copyright\\u00a9 2025, THG PUBLISHING PVT LTD. or its affiliated companies.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 3208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2809, \"end\": 2820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996282934778228, \"rank\": 0.00037184473810772, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BACK TO TOP  Terms & conditions|Institutional Subscriber  Comments have to be in English, and in full sentences.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They cannot be abusive or personal.\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please abide by ourcommunity guidelinesfor posting your comments.\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have migrated to a new commenting platform.\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are already a registered user of The Hindu and logged in, you may continue to engage with our articles.\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3534, \"end\": 3543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Hindu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3220578660572096e-20, \"text\": \"The Hindu\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q23446